There are a few things I can conjure up while you read this sentence. One, you just read *this*. Second, you probably texted someone in the last second, an hour or maybe today.

Live communication between us through *texts/images/gifs* or in more colloquial terms "texting", on a shared platform comes so naturally now, considering the [technology](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc6455) working behind the scenes is in fairly recent history.

